Name: Shroomfish Stew Lv.2
Description2$english: Some mountain mushrooms are used as ingredients, while others become the base for the broth, with fish added at the end to ensure texture—multiple complex preparation methods and meticulously considered layers of seasoning make this dish a threshold for countless chefs on their growth path.

recipes.Name: Shroomfish Stew
recipes.Des:
Crafting yields products Lv.1, Lv.2, and Lv.3 at rates of 50%, 40%, and 10%, respectively.
Some mountain fungi shine as star ingredients, while others transform into an umami-rich broth, finished with flaky fish for sublime texture. This Culinary, with its intricate techniques and meticulously layered seasoning, has made the dish a rite of passage for aspiring chefs.
